== Change Log

=== 1.0.5 (May 10, 2010)
* Fixed calculation of fade duration
* Removed ExampleSprite from SoundControlDemo, used this instead
* Added registerEventListener tp SoundControl
* Added fadeOutAndStopSound to SoundControl
* Check if SoundObject is already playing when calling play()
* Check if _soundChannel exists in stop() in SoundObject

=== 1.0.4 (July 27, 2009)
* Added SoundEvent.STOP_SOUND
* Added getter for volume and pan in SoundObject
* Check if _soundChannel exists in fadeOut() and setter for volume and pan in SoundObject
* Check if sound with id exists for playSound(), stopSound(), fadeInSound() and fadeOutSound() in SoundControl

=== 1.0.3 (July 10, 2009)
* Added SoundEvent that bubbles on default
* Renamed package from de.pixelate.pelikan.sound to de.pixelate.soundcontrol since the Pelikan libary is no longer under active development
* Moved example code into de.pixelate.demo.SoundControlDemo and added graphical equalizer

=== 1.0.2 (July 5, 2009)
* Added fadeInSound and fadeOutSound to SoundControl
* Renamed getSoundFromDictionary to getSound in SoundControl and made it public
* Made setters for volume and pan in SoundObject public and used implict setter function

=== 1.0.1 (Mai 9, 2009)
* Added optional basePath
* Added stopSound to SoundControl
* Used getter/setter for xmlConfig

=== 1.0.0 (February 1, 2009)
* First release.